Name: Greater Kao Rune
Types: Rune
Components: Kao Rune, Level 3 Spell Slot
Description: This rune symbolizes ill intent, lasting suffering, and misfortune. It is commonly known as the rune of curses, allowing those who wield it the ability to inflict calamity upon their foes.SPACESPACEWhile wearing or using an item imbued with this rune, you gain the following feature.SPACECurse of DeathSPACEAs an action, you attempt to curse a target within DISTANCE15-30DISTANCE feet of you with inexorable awareness of their own mortality. The target must succeed on a Wisdom saving throw, or become cursed for TIME2-4TIME rounds. While cursed, the target becomes frightened of all creatures it can see, and you can use a reaction to deal DAMAGE2-4DAMAGEd6 necrotic damage to the target at the start of each of its turns. A creature that succeeds on its saving throw is immune to this effect for the next 24 hours.SPACESPACEYou may invoke this rune a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus before its magic is depleted. The rune will recharge from ambient magic as you complete a long rest. This rune occupies 4 runic attunement slots. Requires Wisdom 16 or greater to attune for a creature who did not craft the rune.
